<BR>
Farming is a system of GREED. It can quite easily be combated if VI had any brains at all... Make all items LORE (1 per person) and most importantly, if you cannot USE an item, you cannot POSSESS that item. Quite simple. Economy is not ruined because loot keeps dropping, but people who NEED an item will be able to get items MUCH easier. Take a good idea for once, VI. If your so-called 'economy' gets a little worse, then increase the classes that can use an item. Is this idea too hard??? NO! The fact that items are lore means that you will have to get help and go thru lots of porting and trouble to consistently farm items. Everyone has to sleep eventually, and even if you have people helping, everyone can only carry ONE of the item.<BR>
<BR>
Nuff said!
